  "text": "[ ](https://www.accuweather.com/pwa)\n  * [ For Business ](https://afb.accuweather.com)\n  * |\n  * [ Warnings ](https://afb.accuweather.com/accuweather-skyguard)\n  * [ Data Suite ](https://afb.accuweather.com/accuweather-data-suite)\n  * [ Forensics ](https://afb.accuweather.com/accuweather-forensicservices)\n  * [ Advertising ](https://advertising.accuweather.com/for-advertising/digital-advertising/)\n  * [ Superior Accuracy™ ](https://afb.accuweather.com/accuweathers-proven-superior-accuracy)\n\n\n[ ](https://www.accuweather.com/) # [Tokyo, Tokyo 16°C ![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-forecast/226396)\n[![Gamezop.com](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/logos/gamezop.png)](https://www.gamezop.com/?id=lW3pW3)\nLocation  Chevron down\nLocation News Videos\nUse Current Location\nRecent\n[ Tokyo Tokyo ![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) 16° ](https://www.accuweather.com/web-api/three-day-redirect?key=226396&target=)\nNo results found.\nTry searching for a city, zip code or point of interest.\n[ ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/videos)\n[ ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/settings)\n[ Help ](https://support.accuweather.com/faq/)\nTokyo, Tokyo Weather\n[Today](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-forecast/226396) [WinterCast](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/winter-weather-forecast/226396) [Local {stormName} Tracker](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/tropical-weather-forecast/226396?eventkey={eventkey}) [Hourly](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/hourly-weather-forecast/226396) [10-Day](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/10-day-weather-forecast/226396) [Radar](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-radar/226396) [MinuteCast®](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/minute-weather-forecast/226396) [Monthly](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/2263