th & Activities ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/health-activities/226396)\n[ 10 Gale Advisory ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-warnings/226396)\n## [Today's Weather Fri, May 22  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) Windy and cooler with considerable cloudiness; morning showers followed by a shower in spots this afternoon **Hi: 16°** ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/35.svg) Tonight: Breezy this evening; otherwise, partly cloudy **Lo: 12°** ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-today/226396)\n## [ Current Weather  2:08 PM  ![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/weathericons/v2a/12.svg) 16°C RealFeel® 13°  Light rain More Details RealFeel Shade™ 11° Wind NNE 19 km/h Wind Gusts 30 km/h Air Quality Fair ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/current-weather/226396) ### [MINUTECAST® Rain ending in 29 min Now 3:08 PM ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/minute-weather-forecast/226396)\n## Tokyo Weather Radar\n[ ![Tokyo Weather Radar](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-forecast/226396) Static Radar Temporarily Unavailable Thank you for your patience as we work to get everything up and running again. Refresh Page ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/weather-radar/226396)\n[ ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/components/maps/mapping-layers/realvue-satellite.jpg) Clouds ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/satellite/226396) [ ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/components/maps/mapping-layers/temperature.jpg) Temperature ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/current-weather-maps)\n## Hourly Weather\nChevron left\n[ 3 PM  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/7.svg) 15° 49% ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/hourly-weather-forecast/226396?hour=1779429600) [ 4 PM  ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/7.svg) 15°