7) [ Fri 5/29 ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/14.svg) 31° 21° Warm; a little afternoon rain ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/33.svg) Clear and humid ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/daily-weather-forecast/226396?day=8) [ Sat 5/30 ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/2.svg) 30° 20° Sunshine and very warm ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/36.svg) Partly cloudy and humid ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/daily-weather-forecast/226396?day=9) [ Sun 5/31 ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/4.svg) 27° 18° Times of clouds and sun ![](https://www.awxcdn.com/adc-assets/images/weathericons/v2a/34.svg) Clear to partly cloudy ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/daily-weather-forecast/226396?day=10)\n##  Sun & Moon \n![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/weathericons/v2a/1.svg) 14 hrs 13 mins\nRise 4:31 AM\nSet 6:44 PM\n![](https://www.accuweather.com/images/moon-phases/colored/light/WaxingCrescent.svg) Waxing Crescent\nRise 9:50 AM\nSet 12:01 AM\n## [Air Quality See More Air Quality Fair The air quality is generally acceptable for most individuals. However, sensitive groups may experience minor to moderate symptoms from long-term exposure.  ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/air-quality-index/226396)\n##  Allergy Outlook \n[See All](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/health-activities/226396)\n[ Dust & Dander Low Data is not supported in this location ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/jp/tokyo/226396/allergies-weather/226396?name=dust-dander)\nTop Stories\n[ Severe Weather Storms to bring needed rain, but also flood risk to Plains, Southeast 9 hours ago ](https://www.accuweather.com/en/severe-weather/storms-to-bring-beneficial-rain-to-plains-southeast-at-the-risk-of-flooding-damaging-winds/1893539) [ Weather News Southern California fires threaten homes and former nuclear si